Class Project

Object
Project
public class Project extends Object
This entity class represents a Build-To-Order (BTO) project.

  • Constructor Details

    • Project

      public Project(String name, String neighbourhood, Map<FlatType,Integer> initialFlatUnitCounts, Map<FlatType,Double> flatUnitPrices, Date applicationOpenDate, Date applicationCloseDate, HdbManager creatingManager)
      Constructs a new Project object.
      Parameters:
      name - The unique name of the project.
      neighbourhood - The neighbourhood of the project.
      initialFlatUnitCounts - A map containing initial counts for each available FlatType.
      flatUnitPrices - A map containing the selling price for each available FlatType.
      applicationOpenDate - The opening date of applications.
      applicationCloseDate - The closing date of applications.
      creatingManager - The HDB Manager creating this project listing.
